These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
City: marseilles, hannover, liverpool, edinburgh
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, ranch-style, wooden
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bongani, davidoff, siglo
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the siglo-smoker is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
5. the gothic-revival house is between the davidoff-smoker and the person traveling to hannover##2
6. the bongani-smoker is the ranch-style house##1
7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City        | liverpool | edinburgh  | hannover | marseilles  |
| House         | wooden    | gothic-revival  | farmhouse       | ranch-style     |
| Cigar   | davidoff     | bolivar | siglo       | bongani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: snooker, bridge, scrabble, whist
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia, rose, zinnia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, davidoff, alhambra, dannemann
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is between the person who growszinnia and the person playing whist##2
5. the person who growszinnia is the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
7. the person who growsrose is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Game         | bridge | snooker    | whist  | scrabble |
| Flower   | zinnia  | daffodil  | begonia   | rose    |
| Cigar         | davidoff | dannemann | siglo | alhambra      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, lizard, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, may, july, february
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, thriller, satire, sports
1. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching sports movies and the owner of the fish##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet      | fish | goldfish         | rabbit   | lizard    |
| Birthday         | may | february | august | july |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | thriller        | sports      | epic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, documentary, horror
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pepper, kiwi, lime
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, coral, emerald, chestnut
1. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes chestnut and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who likes chestnut is between the person eating broccoli and the person who likes coral##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | comedy   | action | documentary |
| Food         | kiwi | broccoli | pepper    | lime |
| Color     | emerald       | ivory     | chestnut       | coral    |

