.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
City: rome, berlin, hannover, new-york
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, chess, mah-jongg
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, cabbage, cauliflower, raspberry
1. the person eating raspberry is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to berlin##2
2. the person eating raspberry is the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person playing whist##1
7. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating cauliflower and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| City   | rome | new-york      | berlin       | hannover   |
| Game      | canasta   | whist  | mah-jongg | chess     |
| Food      | cabbage     | raspberry | cauliflower        | watermelon |

