.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, pilot, designer, analyst
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, october, march
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, action, western
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the dancer is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching action movies##2
6. the pilot is between the dancer and the designer##2
7. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Job    | designer | pilot  | dancer | analyst      |
| Birthday   | october  | march  | june | december |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller | mystery | action     |

