.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, guinea-pig, turtle
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, dutch, colombian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, rock, disco
1. the fan disco is the dutch##1
2. the fan rock is the indonesian##1
3. the colombian is on the far left##1
4. the japanese is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the fan blues##1
6. the owner of the pony is between the dutch and the colombian##2
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet          | guinea-pig  | pony    | turtle | cat  |
| Nationality   | colombian | japanese       | dutch        | indonesian    |
| Music-Genre         | folk | blues | disco  | rock |

