.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
City: london, new-york, boston, rome
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, old-henry, blend, ritmeester
House: art-deco, farmhouse, modern, victorian
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the victorian house and the person traveling to new-york##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| City         | rome  | new-york | boston | london |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | ritmeester | old-henry   | blend         |
| House           | art-deco | modern  | farmhouse   | victorian      |

