.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, family, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, handball, biathlon
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, apricot, blood-red, green
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes green##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who's sport is volleyball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Movie-Genre          | epic  | romance    | family | martial-arts       |
| Sport         | biathlon | surfing | volleyball  | handball |
| Color   | blood-red   | green      | apricot  | ivory     |

