1. the tower house is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to prague and the futuristic house##2
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the modern house is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the tower house##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| City          | san-francisco      | hannover | venice | prague |
| House         | tower   | futuristic  | cape-cod | modern |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | parkour   | handball | skiing |

