.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, april, november
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, billiard, canasta
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, bellflower, begonia, daffodil
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing billiard##2
4. the person playing billiard is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person playing billiard is the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person playing canasta is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday    | november  | april | august | february     |
| Game   | scrabble | billiard   | canasta  | mah-jongg    |
| Flower     | bellflower        | daffodil       | marigold      | begonia |

