.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
City: miami, liverpool, marseilles, berlin
4 different games are played: chess, poker, backgammon, canasta
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, may, november
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person playing poker##2
4. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City   | berlin | marseilles     | liverpool | miami       |
| Game      | backgammon  | canasta | chess  | poker |
| Birthday        | november  | april      | may        | february      |

