.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, scientist, firefighter, security-guard
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, cucumber, kale, tomato
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, orange, lilac, yellow
1. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes yellow is between the firefighter and the person eating lettuce##2
3. the scientist is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the electrician is the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the security-guard is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | electrician | security-guard  | firefighter       | scientist   |
| Food      | lettuce     | kale | cucumber | tomato |
| Color        | lilac        | yellow | grey     | orange |

