There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, purple, mauve, red
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, whist, bridge
1. the person drinking fanta is the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing bridge is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes red##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking almond-milk##2
6. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing billiard is between the person playing bridge and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
