5. the mechanic is on the left of the teacher##1
6. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who likes amber##2
7. the person who likes purple is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
