.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, rock-climbing, card-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, milk, coffee
4 different games are played: scrabble, chess, billiard, snooker
1. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
5. the person playing snooker is the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | card-games | skydiving | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Beverage         | juice       | iced-tea     | milk   | coffee   |
| Game   | scrabble | chess | billiard | snooker |

 